              seizure.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><b><a href="http://www.michbar.org/opinions/home.html?/opinions/district/2001/090501/12359.html">Full 
              Text Opinion</a></b></font></p>
            <hr>
